,"tid":21670,"uid":20117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"HKE位真心窄<br />\n冇下次<br />\n屌你重窄過香草<br />\n比多少少搭jetstar好過<br />\n由其凌晨機真係頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過平靚正真心不存在<br />\n只係睇食幾多舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa9158eba9821d5e1bf64a899ecd56d234e8454","tid":21670,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:52:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去程問題係地勤公司，搭其他航空公司用以間都會有以個問題<br />\n<br />\n回程就係人種問題加HKE 問題。人就唔駛我講。強烈要求HKE 應該參考人地Ryanair 果種嚴格執行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解HKE 好少tag 手提行李奇倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRyanair EasyJet 會係閘口拎啲喼放落Bulk 咁就唔洗阻住起飛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為咁做既話 以香港人本性 應該個個喼都要寄倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c178c2fccfd9465ab7332baa0e611740e084379","tid":21670,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>收皮啦 你坐緊既係廉航<br />\n唔係國泰 坐得budget airline<br />\n冇service 是常識吧？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到底我幾時有投訴人地冇service?<br />\n<br />\n反而係hke service&quot;太好&quot;<br />\n人地無位放行李都要幫佢清櫃<br />\n唔索性貴客自理? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我反而見過UO空姐會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個d一袋二袋又嘈冇位擺野既客</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次有對情侶遲上機<br />\n個空少初頭好好心機幫佢搵位擺行李<br />\n同佢塞咗三袋之後條仔仲拎多兩袋話仲有<br />\n個空少即刻好炆叫佢自己放櫈底<br />\n搭過幾次都無見過會執走其他客嘅行李幫人擺"},{"pid":"e832d63e4b3b20ea89a76fe7ec966cc1a269a5e8","tid":21670,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:07:49.000Z","msg":"係咪我問題？<br />\n覺得短途uo好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：搭過阿聯x"},{"pid":"0f02911df32fffbba5b79cda324659929b8b68f5","tid":21670,"uid":47264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除左郁你行李叫你擺櫈底覺得有問題之外，其他都冇乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n利申: 窮L又要去旅行，一年搭幾次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛機未停定拎行李都冇問題？<br />\n我真係第一次係香港見到d咁既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然唔關航空公司事<br />\n不過廉航較多呢d低質素旅客<br />\n幾影響旅行心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔止UO啦，搭CX都大把呢D客</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未停定拎行李好似冇見過，多數係差唔多泊到位就企晒起身，feel到停左就即刻開行李櫃，拎野等開艙門，總之分秒必爭個隻咁<br />\n一停就企起身我覺得可以理解，畢竟都坐係度屈住幾個鐘</blockquote><br />\n係香港走得快咪又係要等行理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔明咁急做乜"},{"pid":"5bc0d99d359e32591b5c93844561eaee61b8d0f2","tid":21670,"uid":21911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:22:25.000Z","msg":"有fd叫我一齊搭廉航去旅行<br />\n我聽到去唔太想 去旅行係享受 <br />\n但廉航質素真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8644cdde98a57152aa4afaa329a09bb0595d9330","tid":21670,"uid":12533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:38:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除左郁你行李叫你擺櫈底覺得有問題之外，其他都冇乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n利申: 窮L又要去旅行，一年搭幾次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛機未停定拎行李都冇問題？<br />\n我真係第一次係香港見到d咁既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然唔關航空公司事<br />\n不過廉航較多呢d低質素旅客<br />\n幾影響旅行心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔止UO啦，搭CX都大把呢D客</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未停定拎行李好似冇見過，多數係差唔多泊到位就企晒起身，feel到停左就即刻開行李櫃，拎野等開艙門，總之分秒必爭個隻咁<br />\n一停就企起身我覺得可以理解，畢竟都坐係度屈住幾個鐘</blockquote><br />\n係香港走得快咪又係要等行理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔明咁急做乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我搭廉航好少寄行李 落機過關真係即刻走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係等行李真係等到天黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe27b06fb4591a0e59cb48d3580ccf864ee8db7","tid":21670,"uid":12533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:43:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>收皮啦 你坐緊既係廉航<br />\n唔係國泰 坐得budget airline<br />\n冇service 是常識吧？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到底我幾時有投訴人地冇service?<br />\n<br />\n反而係hke service&quot;太好&quot;<br />\n人地無位放行李都要幫佢清櫃<br />\n唔索性貴客自理? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我反而見過UO空姐會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個d一袋二袋又嘈冇位擺野既客</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次有對情侶遲上機<br />\n個空少初頭好好心機幫佢搵位擺行李<br />\n同佢塞咗三袋之後條仔仲拎多兩袋話仲有<br />\n個空少即刻好炆叫佢自己放櫈底<br />\n搭過幾次都無見過會執走其他客嘅行李幫人擺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好多呢d西客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本返黎見過有人又係好遲上機，好多袋野，空姐指示佢搵位攝d家當，佢仲要懶巴閉話，呢袋生果黎架唔壓得乜乜乜<br />\n我心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地比你上機仲有位你擺算你好彩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ee1cf61b4eb4c37971d21e31b9309eba3d5d93","tid":21670,"uid":30150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:26:02.000Z","msg":"回程行李架好嚴重<br />\n特係一家大細同師9<br />\n又遲上機又大堆行李放架<br />\n<br />\n第一次中伏後（d野要放地下前面），<br />\n之後5 6次都係早d上機放野<br />\n如果要求你將野放前面<br />\n就話唔壓得易爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話無你符<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n親自經歷"},{"pid":"fc7a8716e624b7fc5eb1799ba5d7e5176cd7c52e","tid":21670,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T23:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回程行李架好嚴重<br />\n特係一家大細同師9<br />\n又遲上機又大堆行李放架<br />\n<br />\n第一次中伏後（d野要放地下前面），<br />\n之後5 6次都係早d上機放野<br />\n如果要求你將野放前面<br />\n就話唔壓得易爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話無你符<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n親自經歷</blockquote><br />\n我有hand carry都會早啲排隊上機<br />\n廢事比人掉左個gip唔知去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e219535e349c05ac22ae48edc61fb222d4fe2a8","tid":21670,"uid":13809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T23:34:42.000Z","msg":"同意 坐廉航啲人牛屎啲<br />\n利申 坐廉航"},{"pid":"4b4dfa139ccadd266ca200640c8376fc80ae0f30","tid":21670,"uid":55846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T23:56:08.000Z","msg":"外國d廉航見爆會㨂人免費托運行李⋯"},{"pid":"cd6e29274732ad8342efd50c31cca5ac88527422","tid":21670,"uid":24635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:14:10.000Z","msg":"坐過一次頂唔順 啲位太窄"},{"pid":"9bfa480b5c12cd90e829bc5db7ea279723a65b7e","tid":21670,"uid":6018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我坐過十幾次都唔覺有問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾百蚊來回連稅去到日本仲想點<br />\n唔係無錢搭因航或者買service，而係睇有無必要姐<br />\n坐3個鐘機訓醒就落機，要咁多service把撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 月入幾皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其他原因係當你去多過7日就覺得廉航抵好多"},{"pid":"c7d2dc019d8d3237b713fb367a2db2ee7a7457a1","tid":21670,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":